  	    "headline": "A Candid Conversation with Jerry Brown, The Once--And Future?--Governor Moonbeam",
  	    "alternativeHeadline": "Next month, irate California voters will go the polls to decide if their next leader should be the same starry-eyed, hot-tempered Zen Buddhist who pulled the state back from the abyss three decades ago. A candid GQ+A with Jerry Brown",
  	    "url": "http://gq.com/story/jerry-brown-interview-california-governer-election",
  	    "image": ["http://media.gq.com/photos/558306ff3655c24c6c9570d2/master/pass/news-and-politics-2010-10-jerry-brown-jerry-brown_300x430.jpg"],
  	    "thumbnailUrl": "http://media.gq.com/photos/558306ff3655c24c6c9570d2/master/pass/news-and-politics-2010-10-jerry-brown-jerry-brown_300x430.jpg",
